FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781547074
OL,3,CTwo men found guilty over arson
OL,4,Cattacks on properties linked to PM
OL,6,FUkrainian Roman Lavrynovych, 22, and
OL,7,FRomanian Stanislav Carpiuc, 27, were
OL,8,Ffound guilty of plotting to damage
OL,9,Fproperty after a jury deliberated for
OL,10,Fseven-and-a-half hours.
OL,12,FCo-defendant Petro Pochynok, 35, was
OL,13,Fcleared of the same charge.
OL,15,FMr Lavrynovych was also convicted of
OL,16,Fdamaging two properties by fire, being
OL,17,Freckless as to whether life was
OL,18,Fendangered, on May 11 and 12 last year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
