PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781547074
OL,3,CTwo men found guilty over arson
OL,4,Cattacks on properties linked to PM
OL,6,FMr Justice Garnham remanded the
OL,7,Fdefendants into custody to be
OL,8,Fsentenced on Friday.
OL,10,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FPolice arrested the defendants within
OL,16,Fa week of the attacks ordered by a
OL,17,FTelegram contact called El Money.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781547074
OL,3,CTwo men found guilty over arson
OL,4,Cattacks on properties linked to PM
OL,6,FThe anonymous Russian speaker had
OL,7,Foffered Mr Lavrynovych #3,000 in
OL,8,Fcryptocurrency if the attacks were
OL,9,Ffilmed and got on the news.
OL,11,FFollowing the convictions, Commander
OL,12,FHelen Flanagan, head of Counter
OL,13,FTerrorism Policing (CTP) London, said
OL,14,Fthere was nothing to indicate El Money
OL,15,Fwas a "state threat".
OL,17,FHowever, she said that the motivation
OL,18,Fbehind the attacks had been to "cause
OL,19,Fconcern" and "disruption" in the
OL,20,Fcommunity within the UK and "fear" for
OL,21,Fthe prime minister.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781547074
OL,3,CTwo men found guilty over arson
OL,4,Cattacks on properties linked to PM
OL,6,FThe court heard how Mr Lavrynovych was
OL,7,Ffirst tasked by El Money to set light
OL,8,Fto the Toyota Rav4 on May 8 last year.
OL,10,FHe had tried to rope in Mr Pochynok to
OL,11,Ffilm it after first approaching his
OL,12,Ffriend Mr Carpiuc, jurors had heard.
OL,14,FThree nights later, a blaze was
OL,15,Freported at a house in nearby
OL,16,FEllington Street in Islington, which
OL,17,Fwas managed by a company of which the
OL,18,FPM had once been a director and
OL,19,Fshareholder.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781547074
OL,3,CTwo men found guilty over arson
OL,4,Cattacks on properties linked to PM
OL,6,FJurors were shown a video shot by Mr
OL,7,FLavrynovych of a lit match being
OL,8,Fthrown onto accelerant on the doorstep
OL,9,Fof the address.
OL,11,FA resident of the top-floor flat was
OL,12,Fwoken by the smell of smoke about half
OL,13,Fan hour later and escaped to the roof
OL,14,Fto call the fire brigade.
OL,16,FProsecutor Duncan Atkinson KC said the
OL,17,Ffire spread to the hallway inside the
OL,18,Fbuilding, posing an "obvious" risk to
OL,19,Fthe occupants of the four flats.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781547074
OL,3,CTwo men found guilty over arson
OL,4,Cattacks on properties linked to PM
OL,6,FIn the early hours of May 12 last
OL,7,Fyear, the PM's former home in Kentish
OL,8,FTown was targeted.
OL,10,FHis sister-in-law Judith Alexander,
OL,11,Fwho lived there with her partner and
OL,12,Fdaughter, said in a statement: "All of
OL,13,Fa sudden I heard two bangs. It was
OL,14,Fvery loud and sounded like two wheelie
OL,15,Fbins had been thrown at the door."
OL,17,F"I did not see anyone on the street
OL,18,Fbut when I looked down, I saw smoke
OL,19,Fand an orange glow where the front
OL,20,Fdoor was."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781547074
OL,3,CTwo men found guilty over arson
OL,4,Cattacks on properties linked to PM
OL,6,FAs thick smoke crept upstairs, Ms
OL,7,FAlexander said she had tried to call
OL,8,Fher sister Victoria, the PM's wife.
OL,10,FShe described her fear at the thought
OL,11,Fof "what might have happened" had she
OL,12,Fnot woken up.
OL,14,FIn the aftermath of the attacks, El
OL,15,FMoney encouraged Mr Lavrynovych to
OL,16,Fflee, saying: "Look, you attacked the
OL,17,Fhome of a very high-ranking person in
OL,18,FBritain. I'll send you money, you need
OL,19,Fto leave the city.
OL,26,@xD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781547074
OL,3,CTwo men found guilty over arson
OL,4,Cattacks on properties linked to PM
OL,6,F"If the police detain you, secretly
OL,7,Fwrite the word, 'geranium' and I'll
OL,8,Fsend a lawyer to you, I'll give you
OL,9,Fmoney for a week and a new phone. We
OL,10,Fwon't be in touch for a week."
OL,12,FMr Lavrynovych, of Sydenham, south
OL,13,FLondon, was charged on May 15 last
OL,14,Fyear.
OL,16,FTwo days later, Mr Carpiuc was stopped
OL,17,Fat Luton Airport as he waited for a
OL,18,Fflight to Romania
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781547074
OL,3,CTwo men found guilty over arson
OL,4,Cattacks on properties linked to PM
OL,6,FIn his defence, Mr Lavrynovych
OL,7,Fadmitted setting fire to the property
OL,8,Fbut claimed he had been threatened by
OL,9,FEl Money.
OL,11,FThe true identity of El Money remains
OL,12,Fa mystery but Mr Lavrynovych said he
OL,13,Fbelieved him to be "powerful" with
OL,14,Fpolitical connections.
OL,16,FPreviously, El Money had tasked him to
OL,17,Fpaint racist graffiti on an Islamic
OL,18,Fcommunity centre and post anti-Muslim
OL,19,Ffliers around for money.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781547074
OL,3,CTwo men found guilty over arson
OL,4,Cattacks on properties linked to PM
OL,6,FHotel worker Mr Carpiuc, from Romford,
OL,7,Feast London, said he had refused to
OL,8,Fget involved and told Mr Lavrynovych
OL,9,Fthe plan was "stupid" and illegal.
OL,11,FHis former housemate, Mr Pochynok, who
OL,12,Fwas working in construction and as a
OL,13,FHarrods delivery driver, told jurors
OL,14,Fthat he did not know about the car
OL,15,Farson plan until it was too late.
OL,26,@qD@NOUqD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
